<h1>Commune</h1>

<figure>
<a href="img/00.jpg"><img src="img/logo/300x300.jpg"/></a>
</figure>

<p>
A <b>commune</b> (the French word appearing in the 12th century from Medieval Latin communia, meaning a large gathering of people sharing a common life; from Latin communis, things held in common) is an intentional community of people living together, sharing common interests, property, possessions, resources, and, in some communes, work and income. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Commune">Wikipedia</a>
</p>

